StarFlier:

She tapped the bot on the head with her tail to make sure it would 
remain out cold until they got to where ever it was they were going 
to.  She tried to get the bot to sit up so they could carry 
it. "Grrr, it's a tad heavier than I thought it would be. Well, let's 
get going. How are we going to get it back to your home? Can we call 
a taxi shuttle?"
